To build the project, simply clone the recommender branch and compile with:

scalac -d bin src/*/*.scala

To run:

scala -cp bin main.Main <dataset_path>

<dataset_path> is something like dataset_mod5_342k.dat

The options -Dactors.corePoolSize=X -Dactors.maxPoolSize=X can be used to set the number of cores use to X-1 (X=3 means 2 cores)

You can find more information in our project report